quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  79,27,Eentum eﾅ歹ddu halkan emissemaﾂｴu benaha
  79,28,Refeﾂｴa semkeha fesevvaha
  79,29,Ve aﾄ殳aﾅ歹 leyleha ve ahrece duhaha
  79,30,Velﾂｴarda baﾂｴde zalike dehaha
  79,31,Ahrece minha aeha ve merﾂｴaha
  79,32,Velcibale ersaha
  79,33,Metaﾂｴan lekum ve lienﾂｴamikum
  79,34,Feiza caetittammetulkubra
  79,35,Yevme yetezekkerulﾂｴinsanu ma seﾂｴa
  79,36,Ve burrizetilcehﾄｱymu limen yera
  79,37,Feemma men taﾄ歛
  79,38,Ve aserelhayateddunya
  79,39,Feinnelcahﾄｱyme hiyelmeﾂｴva
  79,40,Ve emma men hafe mekame rabbihi ve nehennefse ﾂｴanilheva
  79,41,Feinnelcennete hiyel meﾂｴva
  79,42,Yesﾂｴeluneke ﾂｴanissaﾂｴati eyyane mursaha
  79,43,Fiyme ente min zikraha
  79,44,ﾄｰla rabbike muntehaha
  79,45,ﾄｰnnema ente munziru men yahﾅ歛ha
  79,46,Keennehum yevme yerevneha lem yelbesu illa ﾂｴaﾅ殃yyeten ev duhaha